### Tournament of Power API Testing

#### 1. Get Maximum Rounds
GET http://localhost:5235/api/tournament/max-rounds?participantCount=12

#### 2. Get Remaining Pairs
GET http://localhost:5235/api/tournament/remaining-pairs?participantCount=12&roundsPlayed=3

#### 3. Generate Round Pairs
POST http://localhost:5235/api/tournament/round
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Round": 2,
    "Participants": [
        { "Id": 1, "Name": "Goku" },
